    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>
      Hello! I'm Hamideh Rezvani Alanagh, a researcher passionate about creating nature-inspired materials that address challenges in health and the environment.
    </p>
    <p>
      My work bridges chemistry, soft matter physics, and biomaterials science to design dynamic, sustainable solutions. From studying biomolecular assemblies to engineering responsive materials for therapeutics, agriculture, and water treatment, I focus on how understanding nature can help us build a better world.
